{"tid":1746559,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消防處回應: 佩戴名牌係optional","createTime":"2019-11-22T19:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T19:53:00.000Z","uid":285243,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"88a771c73e70fb7ac4003f72bae69801ae02798a","tid":1746559,"uid":285243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:46:38.000Z","msg":"【消防處回應】<br />\n<br />\n就近日香港聚眾活動及暴力事件的情況，消防處救護員會的代表向管方表達在執勤時展示個人名字的憂慮。考慮到近幾個月來，個人資料被「起底」及網絡欺凌行為的情況不斷增加，本處屬員及其家人對此有所擔憂，處方昨日發出通知，各救護人員在執行行動職務時，均不需要佩戴名牌，直至另行通知。<span style=\"color: red;\">若救護人員沒有上述的擔憂，可選擇繼續佩戴名牌。</span><br />\n<br />\n管方希望有關安排能回應前線同事的訴求，減低他們於工作時的憂慮。同時，救護人員一向以救護車為出勤單位，公眾除了可以車號作識別，本處對在車上當值的救護人員資料(包括姓名和編號)亦有清晰明確的紀錄可供核對。移除名牌不應影響公眾人士確認本處的救護人員。同時，在一般情況下，如市民提出要求，本處人員會提供其姓名及職銜。<br />\n<br />\n#香港消防處 #HKFSD<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPQGXKm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPQGXKm.jpg&h=825488d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e35c32c8b98f7ab3e7e55afe73c44695d3d4de17","tid":1746559,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X7iQbsL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX7iQbsL.png&h=28be2a98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71c9426d08a02d4546045169446e200d959737bb","tid":1746559,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:48:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5JH5KUu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5JH5KUu.jpg&h=28642846&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb703a2d70058264a50cd20c1474dbb5e190d8df","tid":1746559,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:48:42.000Z","msg":"消防黑警，玩乜鳩起到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16db3b22c06ae68b6c41b0e7cba6c8f8f8e7cb51","tid":1746559,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:49:48.000Z"